divs: Sighting DetailsI was drinking coffe with my friend at the lake Jarun in Zagreb (Croatia),i took 3 pictures (left,right and last middle),there was nothing unusual i just wanted to capture the nature,so when i got home and look at the pictures the middle picture had a black spot and i thought i burned my phone lcd display and i panickly zoomed to see if the display was damaged.To my suprise after zooming the object i realised i captchured something wierd.
